1
00:00:17,833 --> 00:00:19,291
[TV NEWSCASTER A] The third
floor of the housing complex,

2
00:00:19,375 --> 00:00:22,000
roughly 20 square meters,
was consumed in the fire,

3
00:00:22,083 --> 00:00:24,208
but there appear to have
been no injuries.

4
